txt.en: Defeat many Orcs, half-orcs, and goblins in the Wildwood.

Vicious Orcs, goblins, and half-orcs have infiltrated the Wildwood, squatting in ruins and abandoned settlements. They grow in strength and numbers, and threaten to spill over the boundaries of the Wildwood.
